DESCRIPTION
===========

Reverses the bytes of a file. Mirros is written in bash.


DOWNLOAD MIRROR
===============

git clone https://github.com/guelfoweb/mirror.git


TO USE mirror
============

   # cd mirror
   # bash mirror


Alternatively, set executable permissions on mirror file

   # cp mirror /usr/local/bin/mirror
   # chmod a+x /usr/local/bin/mirror
   # mirror


OTHER
=====

